		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Yeah I guess you're right.  I was thinking he'd want to make sure he had it in the original case and be hacking one up anyways.  
<br />
<br />But retrozone's boards fit in the original cases.  So he could just but the new board in the old case and hang on to the original board.  That way it would still have the original cart's casing as a disguise.  I know the powerpak was brought up, but if she realized it wasn't the original cart it wouldn't be as surprising.

		

